<div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">NickPicks is a participant in the <strong>Amazon Services LLC Associates Program</strong>, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. This means that if you click on certain links on our site and make a purchase, we may receive a commission — at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>.</p>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">Our Editorial Independence</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Our affiliate relationships never influence our editorial opinions. We recommend products because we believe they deliver genuine value to our readers — not because they pay higher commissions. In fact, some of our most highly recommended products carry lower commission rates than alternatives we ranked lower.</p>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">How It Works</h2>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li>When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, Amazon tracks the referral.</li>
    <li>We receive a small percentage of the sale (typically 1–10% depending on product category).</li>
    <li>The price you pay is identical whether or not you use our link.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">FTC Compliance</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's guidelines, all articles on NickPicks that contain affiliate links include a disclosure notice at the top of the article. We believe in transparent disclosure and full compliance with all applicable FTC regulations.</p>
  <p style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:2rem">Last updated: June 2026</p>
